Weaknesses: Heavily relies on pure brute force of their infantries in most cases.

Name: Central Realm
Strengths: Excellet late heavy infantries and cavalries.

Name: Undying Horde
Strengths: Can easily field an unstoppable horde.
Weaknesses: Weak ranged units. Somewhat static capability.
Relies on magical powess to compete in late period.

Name: Doll Family
Weaknesses: Individually weak. No units can truly hold on their own.
Expensive cost to purchase and maintain for most units.

Name: Highland Clan
Strengths: Superb shock units for all periods.
Weaknesses: Has no air units. Most units focus on offense rather than defense.
Lack speed even for cavalry units.
Most units are relatively weak in melee combat strength

Name: Wee Alliance
Strengths: Numerous and versatile. Capable early units.
Weaknesses: Lacks specialised and heavy armour units.
